arch = st_sfc(st_point(c(-83.375284, 33.957525))) %>% st_set_crs(4326)
setwd(paste(getwd(), "/Thesis Data", sep=""))
sales <- map(paste("Sales/", list.files("Sales"), sep = ""), read_csv, col_types = "cccnffdfinnf") %>% bind_rows() %>% clean_names() %>% mutate(sale_date = mdy(sale_date)) %>% filter(parcel_id %in% cd_shapes$Name | parcel_id %in% buffered_shapes$Name) %>% mutate(cd_zoned = parcel_id %in% cd_shapes$Name)
sales %<>% left_join(rbind(cd_shapes, buffered_shapes), by = c("parcel_id" = "Name")) %>% select(-"Description")
plot(st_geometry(st_transform(buffered_shapes, crs = 3857)), col = 'blue', bgMap = bg_map)
plot(st_geometry(st_transform(cd_shapes, crs = 3857)), col = 'red', add = TRUE)
plot(st_transform(st_geometry(arch), 3857), add = TRUE)
legend(x=-9282599, y = 4021671, legend = c("C-D Zoned", "Other Zoned"), fill = c('red', 'blue'))

sales %<>% mutate(cd_zoned = parcel_id %in% cd_shapes$Name,
                  moratorium = sale_date > "2017-02-07")
sales$arch_distance <- as.numeric(st_distance(sales$geometry, arch))
## st_as_s2(): dropping Z and/or M coordinate
ggplot()+
  geom_sf(data = sales$geometry, aes(fill = sales$arch_distance))

mdl <- lm(sale_price ~ sale_date + acres + year_built + square_ft + price_per_square_ft + cd_zoned + arch_distance + cd_zoned*moratorium, data = sales)
